title: Weekly Roundup: Friday, February 5
description: This week, analysis of Thursday night's Democratic debate and a look at the state of the race for 2016 (and Marcomentum) just days away from the New Hampshire Primary. This episode: campaign reporter Asma Khalid and congressional correspondent Susan Davis join hosts Sam Sanders and Tamara Keith. Find the team on Twitter @asmamk, @DaviSusan, @samsanders, and @tamarakeithNPR, and at npr.org/politics — or email the show at nprpolitics@npr.org.
